artifacts/v6_arch_sweep/
# v7 sweep outputs (Stage 2 conditional: 3-arch x 7-algo x 10-seed x 5-alpha FL)
artifacts/v7_fl_arch_sweep/
# Stage 1 post-hoc audit cells (lr-ablation, T_inner ablation, etc.)
artifacts/v6_arch_sweep_audit/
# Auto-generated paper-result aggregations (regenerated by aggregate_v{5,6,7}_results.py)
artifacts/RESULTS_V5.md
